&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;nc &lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cDovL2V4YW1wbGUuY29t&#34;&gt;example.com&lt;/span&gt; 8181 你会 make make 吗？&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly90d2VsdmVlZWUtbm90ZS5vc3MtY24tYmVpamluZy5hbGl5dW5jcy5jb20vZmlsZS9iY3RmMjAyNS9NYWtlTWFrZXJNYWluLnB5&#34;&gt;https://twelveeee-note.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/file/bctf2025/MakeMakerMain.py&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
