&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly9qdWVqaW4uY24vcG9zdC82ODQ0OTAzOTM2NzE4MDEyNDMwI2hlYWRpbmctMjI=&#34;&gt;https://juejin.cn/post/6844903936718012430#heading-22&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly9qYXZhZ3VpZGUuY24vZGlzdHJpYnV0ZWQtc3lzdGVtL3Byb3RvY29sL2NhcC1hbmQtYmFzZS10aGVvcmVtLmh0bWwjYmFzZS0lRTclOTAlODYlRTglQUUlQkElRTQlQjglODklRTglQTYlODElRTclQjQlQTA=&#34;&gt;https://javaguide.cn/distributed-system/protocol/cap-and-base-theorem.html#base - 理论三要素&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
